 min\/100°C\/speed <b>."},{"content":"Add remaining 200 g water, fish sauce, soy sauce, lime juice, salt and pepper then, with simmering basket in place of measuring cup, cook <b>30 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>."},{"content":"Place noodles in a glass bowl, cover with boiling water and leave to soak for 15 minutes."},{"content":"Strain beef stock in mixing bowl through simmering basket into a large jug. Discard contents in simmering basket."},{"content":"Drain rice noodles through simmering basket and divide evenly between 6 serving bowls."},{"content":"Place beef fillet slices on top of rice noodles, then pour over hot beef stock (the hot stock will cook the beef slightly)."},{"content":"Garnish with spring onions, coriander, mint, basil, bean sprouts, chillies and limes. Serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If you cannot buy beef bones pre-cut into pieces, please ask your butcher to cut your beef bones into pieces for you. We do not recommend you do this yourself at home."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 45m","6 portions"]}